(56, 1, '2018-10-18 16:21:48', '2018-10-18 16:21:48', 'Información sobre hospitalización', 'Hospitalización', 'Where does it come from?\r\nContrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature,', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hospitalizacion', '', '', '2018-10-30 01:54:06', '2018-10-30 01:54:06', '', 9, 'http://localhost:8888/laMisericordiaSite/?page_id=56', 0, 'page', '', 0),
