(327, 1, '2018-11-01 21:52:31', '2018-11-01 21:52:31', '<div class=\"form-group\">\r\n<label> Tu nombre (obligatorio)\r\n    [text* your-name class:form-control class:md] </label>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n<label> Tu email (obligatorio)\r\n    [email* your-email class:form-control class:md] </label>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n<label> ¿Cuál es el motivo? (obligatorio)\r\n[select* menu-tipo-pqr id:pqr-type-dropdown class:form-control class:md \"Queja\" \"Reclamo\" \"Petición\" \"Felicitación\"] </label>\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n<label> ¿Qué quieres escribirnos?\r\n    [textarea your-message class:form-control ] </label>\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n[submit class:btn class:btn-primary class:btn-lg class:btn-block class:pink class:no-border \"Send\"]\r\n </div>\n1\n\"[menu-tipo-pqr]\" al Hospital La Misericordia Calarcá\n[your-name] <siau@hospitalcalarca.gov.co>\nsiau@hospitalcalarca.gov.co\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [menu-tipo-pqr]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Hospital La Misericordia Calarcá (https://hospitalcalarca.gov.co/)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nHospital La Misericordia Calarcá \"[your-subject]\"\nHospital La Misericordia Calarcá <sebasz1000@gmail.com>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Hospital La Misericordia Calarcá (http://localhost:8888/laMisericordiaSite)\nReply-To: sebasz1000@gmail.com\n\n\n\nTu mensaje ha sido enviado. Muchas gracias!\nHubo un error al enviar tu mensaje. Por favor, inténtalo de nuevo\nUno o más campos que llenaste están incorrectos o faltantes.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nEste dato es obligatorio\nEste campo es muy largo\nEste campo es muy corto\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nEl e-mail que ingresaste no es válido\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Contact form 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2018-11-02 00:42:47', '2018-11-02 00:42:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/laMisericordiaSite/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=327', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
